  fhir:description [ fhir:v "IMMZ.D18.S.Cholera.WC-rBS vaccine 3-dose schedule\nWhole cell-recombinant B subunit (WC-rBS) vaccine (Dukoral), 3-dose schedule for clients aged 2–5 years"] ; # 
